        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 16. Epitranus clavatus (Fabricius) (female) A fore wing (parts of wing membrane and MV and STV magnified) B, C hind leg, excluding coxa (outer and ventral views respectively) D metasoma (dorsal view)." , "Figure 15. Epitranus clavatus (Fabricius) (female) A head (frontal view) B lower part of face showing frontal lobe (frontal view) C antennal pedicel and flagellum D propodeum and part of metasomal petiole (dorsal view)." , "Figure 14. Epitranus clavatus (Fabricius) (female) A, B habitus (lateral and dorsal views respectively)." ;
